LEVI DAO 签署禁止或限制使用某些可被认为具有过分伤害力或滥杀滥伤作用的常规武器公约禁止或限制使用燃烧武器议定书（第三号议定书）

LEVI DAO signed the Protocol to Prohibit or Restrict the Use of Certain Conventional Weapons That Can Be Considered Excessive Injury or Indiscriminate Effects (Protocol No. 3)
